{"id":146861,"type":2,"name":"霊剣山 星屑たちの宴","name_cn":"从前有座灵剑山","date":"2016-01-08","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/67/4f/146861_OWDcO.jpg","rating":{"rank":7459,"total":891,"count":{"1":16,"2":17,"3":31,"4":110,"5":220,"6":314,"7":134,"8":35,"9":10,"10":4},"score":5.5},"summary":"因彗星陨落，末法大劫而降临的奇才，来自现代世界的穿越者王陆，怀着千年未有的空灵根，踏入灵剑派山门，走上了一条成为智商碾压异界，成为绝世逗逼强者的不寻常路。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>从前有座灵剑山</li><li><span>话数: </span>12</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>2016年1月8日</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期五</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/19440\">国王陛下</a></li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/136\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">鈴木行</a></li><li><span>分镜: </span><a href=\"/person/18\">木村真一郎</a>、<a href=\"/person/136\">鈴木行</a>、<a href=\"/person/22433\">博多正寿</a>、<a href=\"/person/2221\">藤原良二</a></li><li><span>演出: </span><a href=\"/person/14056\">佐藤和磨</a>、<a href=\"/person/26570\">矢花馨</a>、<a href=\"/person/24566\">新子太一</a>、<a href=\"/person/25744\">関大</a>、<a href=\"/person/26569\">鈴木芳成</a>、<a href=\"/person/26571\">千葉孝幸</a>、<a href=\"/person/22518\">秦義人</a>、<a href=\"/person/24637\">黒田晃一郎</a></li><li><span>音乐: </span><a href=\"/person/20702\">川﨑龍</a></li><li><span>人物设定: </span><a href=\"/person/18772\">飯野まこと</a></li><li><span>系列构成: </span><a href=\"/person/136\">鈴木行</a></li><li><span>美术监督: </span><a href=\"/person/19926\">羽根広舟</a></li><li><span>色彩设计: </span><a href=\"/person/19927\">山部一久</a></li><li><span>总作画监督: </span><a href=\"/person/26638\">石井ゆみこ</a></li><li><span>作画监督: </span><a href=\"/person/26638\">石井ゆみこ</a>、<a href=\"/person/55404\">김이성</a>、<a href=\"/person/57714\">野中美希</a>、<a href=\"/person/11706\">飯飼一幸</a>、<a href=\"/person/2884\">石原恵治</a></li><li><span>摄影监督: </span><a href=\"/person/12419\">千葉洋之</a></li><li><span>道具设计: </span><a href=\"/person/51396\">岸川麻美</a></li><li><span>主题歌编曲: </span>岩崎隆一 / <a href=\"/person/13588\">奥山アキラ</a> / 桂子油 / <a href=\"/person/24375\">LBG</a></li><li><span>主题歌作曲: </span><a href=\"/person/8818\">まふまふ</a> / <a href=\"/person/13588\">奥山